2026-04-19 04:39:44,067 | INFO | sqlalchemy.engine.Engine | [cached since 0.003016s ago] ()
2026-04-19 04:39:44,068 | INFO | sqlalchemy.engine.Engine | BEGIN (implicit)
2026-04-19 04:39:44,068 | INFO | sqlalchemy.engine.Engine | 
            SELECT
                strategy,
                COUNT(*)                                        AS total_trades,
                SUM(pnl)                                        AS total_pnl,
                SUM(CASE WHEN pnl > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)       AS wins,
                SUM(CASE WHEN pnl <= 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)      AS losses,
                AVG(pnl)                                        AS avg_pnl,
                MAX(pnl)                                        AS best_trade,
                MIN(pnl)                                        AS worst_trade,
                AVG(price_at_trade)                             AS avg_price
            FROM trades
            WHERE strategy IS NOT NULL
            GROUP BY strategy
            ORDER BY total_pnl DESC
        
